<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.8.9">
<l>eṅku muḷaṉkaṇṇa ṉeṉṟamaka ṉaikkāyn</l>
<l>tiṅkillai yāleṉ ṟiraṇiyaṉ ṟūṇpuṭaippa</l>
<l>vaṅkap poḻutē yavaṉvīyat tōṉṟiyaveṉ</l>
<l>ciṅkap pirāṉperumai yārāyuñ cīrmaittē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is famous, when examined, the greatness of my lion lord</l>
<l>who, when, angry with the son who said “Kṛṣṇa is everywhere”,</l>
<l>Hiraṇya, beat the pillar, saying “[he] is not here!”,</l>
<l>appeared so that he perished there and then.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
